%% Synapse Pipeline

graph LR
    subgraph Ingestion
        A1[Code Files<br/>Python] -->|tree-sitter| B1[RawCodeChunks]
        A2[Knowledge Docs<br/>PDF, DOCX, MD] -->|docling| B2[RawKnowledgeChunks]
    end

    B1 --> C[Normalization<br/>kind · keywords · embed_text]
    B2 --> C

    C --> D[Embedding<br/>L2-normalized vectors]

    D --> E[(Actian VectorAI<br/>cosine KNN + metadata filters)]

    E --> F[Retrieval<br/>code↔knowledge search + LLM explanation]
